filament_end_gcode:
; Filament-specific end gcode 
;END gcode for filament
filament_start_gcode:
; Filament gcode
;M412 D25
;M412 S1  ; Enable Runout
;M900 K0.12 ; Linear advance spring constant - based on sunlu blue petg

{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_MODEL_E3DD.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.4} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.0975{endif}  ; set E3DD advance
{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_MODEL_CYBER.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.4} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.0975{endif}  ; set cybermk2 advance{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*HOTEND_TRONXY_BOWDEN.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==1.0} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.55 SMOOTH_TIME=0.080{endif} ;septembeer 2024
name: Ankun PETG
